## System Prompts

```typescript
const response = await client.messages.create({
  model: "{{OPUS_ID}}",
  max_tokens: 16000,
  system:
    "You are a helpful coding assistant. Always provide examples in Python.",
  messages: [{ role: "user", content: "How do I read a JSON file?" }],
