Also available: \`new ToolUnion(new WebFetchTool20260209())\`, \`new ToolUnion(new MemoryTool20250818())\`. \`WebSearchTool20260209\` optionals: \`AllowedDomains\`, \`BlockedDomains\`, \`MaxUses\`, \`UserLocation\`.

